head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths WINANT, JANINE LOUISE

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths WINANT, JANINE LOUISE

block.p: WINANT-Janine Louise. On August 6, 2000. Of Coventry Farm in Princeton, New Jersey. Wife of the late John G. Winant. Graveside services will be held Friday, August 11 at 11:30AM at Princeton Cemetery, Princeton. Memorial contributions to the ASPCA, The Humane Society of the United States, National Wildlife Federation or the NJ Audubon Society.
